title: Friends With Faith | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Friends With Faith | Joel Osteen
description:
Your faith has the power to bring healing and freedom to those around you. As you speak victory over the lives of others, God will make sure you have everything you need. 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
